title: Was Corona's virus in the United States in early December 2019?
subtitle: Just because the virus might have existed earlier than he thought before doesn't mean it was widespread at the time.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: A study published in November 2020 analysed the anti-sars-Coffo-2 bodies in 2019 blood bank donations and found that the new krona virus might have been present in the United States weeks before scientists realized it.
